A JSON-format string containing the UniqueId and Data values from the wait condition signal(s) for the specified wait condition. For more information about wait condition signals, see Wait Condition Signal JSON Format . Example of a wait condition with two signals: Copy {"Signal1":"Step 1 complete.","Signal2":"Step 2 complete."}
